          "username": "jhh"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2022-01-27 16:58:05.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 6:\n\nMinus-1 this until we reach agreements as I posted on Rashmi's review:\nhttps://gerrit.onap.org/r/c/policy/apex-pdp/+/126762",
        "patchset_number": 6
      },
      {
        "id": "38c0fc50b923adb2cfd130f5e20828e48a11a53a",
